# Example htpasswd file for Radicale (format depends on the image/config).
# If you keep `[auth] type = none` in default.conf, this file is unused.
#
# If you switch to htpasswd auth, generate a real entry and save it to:
#   ~/.calendar/radicale/etc/users
#
# Example (APR1 / MD5):
#   liempo:$apr1$XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX$YYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYY

